# --------------------------------------------------------
**/target/
**/*.jar
**/*.war
**/*.class

# --------------------ECLIPSE IDE FILES-------------------  
**/.classpath
**/.project
**/.settings/
**/.factorypath
**/bin/

# --------------------INTELLIJ IDEA--------------------
**/.idea/
**/*.iml
**/*.iws
**/*.ipr

# --------------------VS CODE--------------------
**/.vscode/

# --------------------SPRING BOOT----------------------
# NEVER commit passwords or secrets!
# ---------------------------------------------------------
**/application-local.yml
**/application-local.properties
**/application-prod.yml
**/application-prod.properties
**/.env

# --------------------LOGS----------------------
*.log
**/logs/
**/log/

